{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/TIL_210517/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"hooks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hooks\" aria-label=\"hooks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hooks</h1>\n<h3 id=\"의미\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%98%EB%AF%B8\" aria-label=\"의미 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>의미</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>기존의 react에서 state 등 코드가 더러웠던 것들을 깔끔하게 해줌</li>\n<li>class가 아닌 functional code로 다 짤 수 있게 해줌</li>\n<li>\n<p>예시 : useState</p>\n<ul>\n<li>기존에 state, this, setState 등등등 여러가지로 코드가 복잡했던 걸 아주 깔끔하게 더 짧은 줄의 코드로 만들어줌</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">function App() {\nconst [item, setItem] = useState(1);\nconst incremental = () =&gt; setItem(item + 1);\nconst decremental = () =&gt; setItem(item - 1);\nreturn (\n&lt;div className=&quot;App&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;h1&gt;Hello CodeSandbox {item}&lt;/h1&gt;\n  &lt;button onClick={incremental}&gt;incremental&lt;/button&gt;\n  &lt;button onClick={decremental}&gt;decremental&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n);\n}</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"linear-gradient\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#linear-gradient\" aria-label=\"linear gradient permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Linear Gradient</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>React Native에서는 자체 CSS 문법이 있는듯?</li>\n<li>Linear Gradient는 배경 색 등이 gradient로 나오게 하는 것</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"style-in-react-native\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-in-react-native\" aria-label=\"style in react native permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style in React Native</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>하나의 element에 두개의 style을 부여하는 법</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;View style={{ ...styles.halfContainer, ...styles.textContainer }}&gt;</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">...</code>을 이용해서, 두개를 사용 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"status-bar\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#status-bar\" aria-label=\"status bar permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Status Bar</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>핸드폰 상단의 Status Bar의 색상 등 스타일을 조정해줄 수 있음 -</li>\n<li>쓰려면 우선 \"react-native\"에서 import</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Hooks 의미 기존의 react에서 state 등 코드가 더러웠던 것들을 깔끔하게 해줌 class가 아닌 functional code로 다 짤 수 있게 해줌 예시 : useState 기존에 state, this, setState 등등등 여러가지로 …","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/TIL_210517/#hooks\">Hooks</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_210517/#%EC%9D%98%EB%AF%B8\">의미</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_210517/#linear-gradient\">Linear Gradient</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_210517/#style-in-react-native\">Style in React Native</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_210517/#status-bar\">Status Bar</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/TIL_210517/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TIL-210517","date":"May 17, 2021","tags":["react","Hooks"],"keywords":["dobedh","Donghyun Kim"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/TIL_210517/","series":[{"slug":"/TIL_210317/","title":"TIL-210429","num":210317},{"slug":"/TIL_210502/","title":"TIL_210502","num":210502},{"slug":"/TIL_210503/","title":"TIL-210503","num":210503},{"slug":"/TIL_210504/","title":"TIL-210505","num":210504},{"slug":"/TIL_210505/","title":"TIL-210506","num":210505},{"slug":"/TIL_210506/","title":"TIL-210504","num":210506},{"slug":"/TIL_210507/","title":"TIL-210507","num":210507},{"slug":"/TIL_210508/","title":"TIL-210508","num":210508},{"slug":"/TIL_210509/","title":"TIL-210509","num":210509},{"slug":"/TIL_210512/","title":"TIL-210512","num":21051